  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Abby Osgood Mandell is glad that &quot;the emigrants for our garden reward your care by their beauty.&quot; While Abby Osgood Mandell has never been a laborer in the anti-slavery cause, her heart &quot;has not been untouched by its claims, nor unmoved by the wrongs of the oppressed.&quot; Although Mr. Mandell &quot;does not fully sympathise with the views of the prominent abolitionists, yet he works in his own way.&quot; Abby Osgood Mandell encloses a contribution for the Liberty Bell, and she hopes to look in at the next bazaar.</subfield>
